headline.print_headline: Britain Puts Stake in Eurostar Up for Sale
headline.main: Britain Puts Stake in Eurostar Up for Sale

lead_paragraph: The British government plans to sell its 40 percent stake in the fast-speed Eurostar train operator that links Britain with the European continent, Chancellor George Osborne announced late on Sunday.
